original_title: NWA Hard Times in New Orleans
overview: On November 12th NWA presents Hard Times in New Orleans live on FITE straight from Frederick J Sigur Civic Center in Chalmette, LA! The event features pro wrestling stars such as NWA Worlds Heavyweight Champion Trevor Murdoch, NWA World Women's Champion Kamille, Matt Cardona, NWA World Television Champion Tyrus, Nick Aldis, Thom Latimer, EC3, Chelsea Green, NWA National Champion ""the Great"" Cyon, Kilynn King, NWA World Tag Team Champions La Rebelion, Local fan favorites Luke & PJ Hawx, and many more!
title: NWA Hard Times in New Orleans
